1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,000
(Watch on www.kisskh.xyz Support Admin)

2
00:00:42,792 --> 00:00:45,170
because we are investigating
the Valtrovi’s.

3
00:00:45,253 --> 00:00:48,423
What do you mean you don’t know them?

4
00:00:48,506 --> 00:00:51,426
Mom and Dad don’t easily trust people.

5
00:00:51,509 --> 00:00:53,303
But for some reason,

6
00:00:53,386 --> 00:00:54,971
you gained their trust right away.

7
00:00:55,055 --> 00:00:56,056
What are you doing here?

8
00:00:56,139 --> 00:00:59,893
Help us to build a case
against the Moraviano’s.

9
00:01:01,644 --> 00:01:03,396
Angelito D. Pinagpala!

10
00:01:03,480 --> 00:01:05,148
-What’s this?
-That’s not mine, sir!

11
00:01:05,231 --> 00:01:07,317
I don’t want to be part of your schemes.

12
00:01:09,194 --> 00:01:11,696
This is also about your brother, Angelito.

13
00:01:28,338 --> 00:01:29,339
Get in.

14
00:01:41,226 --> 00:01:43,061
CZECH CABLE COMPANY

15
00:01:47,941 --> 00:01:50,902
Welcome to our humble abode!

16
00:01:52,695 --> 00:01:54,489
Our surveillance van is nice, right?

17
00:01:54,572 --> 00:01:55,406
It's high-tech!

18
00:01:55,490 --> 00:01:57,283
I personally designed that,

19
00:01:57,367 --> 00:01:58,576
just like Tony Stark.

20
00:02:00,829 --> 00:02:03,123
It was Sianong’s idea to show this to you.

21
00:02:03,206 --> 00:02:05,708
So you can see how serious we are
about our mission.

22
00:02:07,043 --> 00:02:08,711
I already told you

23
00:02:08,795 --> 00:02:10,713
that I don’t want
to get involved in your mission.

24
00:02:25,436 --> 00:02:28,273
This is a raid! This is a raid!

25
00:02:28,356 --> 00:02:29,732
We received information

26
00:02:29,816 --> 00:02:32,902
that your brother was arrested
in a drug den during a buy-bust operation.

27
00:02:33,653 --> 00:02:36,072
And he was caught
with a significant amount of drugs.

28
00:02:36,948 --> 00:02:39,909
Enough for him to be considered
a pusher by the police.

29
00:02:40,743 --> 00:02:41,661
That’s not true.

30
00:02:46,332 --> 00:02:48,293
-Explain that at the police station!
-He could be imprisoned for life.

31
00:02:48,877 --> 00:02:51,462
Especially if it’s proven
that he was involved in the selling

32
00:02:51,546 --> 00:02:53,006
and distribution of illegal drugs.

33
00:02:53,089 --> 00:02:54,591
I said that’s not true!

34
00:02:54,674 --> 00:02:56,342
-Hey!
-Mikoy, wait!

35
00:02:56,426 --> 00:02:57,969
-Mikoy!
-Wait!

36
00:02:58,052 --> 00:02:59,512
Can we talk?

37
00:02:59,596 --> 00:03:01,764
I was showing you that
because I want to help.

38
00:03:01,848 --> 00:03:03,850
I have no idea what really happened.

39
00:03:07,145 --> 00:03:09,439
Just unlucky that he
got caught in the raid.

40
00:03:12,275 --> 00:03:13,818
As if nothing happened.

41
00:03:16,195 --> 00:03:18,239
And he can still continue
the dream you have for him.

42
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:21,075
Don’t mess with me!

43
00:03:21,910 --> 00:03:23,077
Because I know what you’re doing!

44
00:03:23,995 --> 00:03:26,915
You’re behind everything
that’s happening to Angelito.

45
00:03:26,998 --> 00:03:28,041
You’re setting him up,

46
00:03:28,124 --> 00:03:29,667
so I’ll agree to what you want!

47
00:03:31,586 --> 00:03:32,837
Do you really think I’m stupid?

48
00:03:32,921 --> 00:03:34,172
Huh!

49
00:03:34,255 --> 00:03:36,841
Just because I didn’t finish school
means I’m dumb?

50
00:03:38,134 --> 00:03:39,093
Huh?

51
00:03:40,386 --> 00:03:44,140
You have the nerve
to drag my brother into this.

52
00:03:45,350 --> 00:03:46,601
Mr. Pinagpala.

53
00:03:49,979 --> 00:03:51,231
We’re only saying this because

54
00:03:51,314 --> 00:03:53,441
maybe you don’t actually know
your brother that well.

55
00:03:53,524 --> 00:03:54,317
Oh really!

56
00:03:55,151 --> 00:03:56,027
-Come on!
-What do you mean no!

57
00:03:56,110 --> 00:03:57,487
Come on! That's enough!

58
00:04:01,324 --> 00:04:02,158
You’re right!

59
00:04:04,244 --> 00:04:05,870
We set Angelito up.

60
00:04:13,127 --> 00:04:14,963
Were we right to do that?

61
00:04:18,383 --> 00:04:20,134
But if we don't do anything,

62
00:04:21,427 --> 00:04:23,763
more innocent people
will get caught up in the crimes

63
00:04:23,846 --> 00:04:25,932
being committed by
the Moraviano Syndicate and Viktor.

64
00:04:27,100 --> 00:04:28,518
Chiara’s family!

65
00:04:30,311 --> 00:04:32,105
So you left me with no choice.

66
00:04:37,026 --> 00:04:38,528
Will you help us?

67
00:04:40,822 --> 00:04:42,699
Or will your brother
spend the rest of his life in prison?

68
00:04:52,375 --> 00:04:53,626
This is what I’ll do.

69
00:04:54,627 --> 00:04:56,254
I’ll tell Chiara the truth.

70
00:04:57,046 --> 00:04:59,048
And I’ll tell her mom and dad

71
00:04:59,632 --> 00:05:01,175
about the bullshit you’re doing!

72
00:05:02,343 --> 00:05:04,679
And if it’s true that
they’re syndicate members

73
00:05:04,762 --> 00:05:06,431
and completely ruthless,

74
00:05:08,182 --> 00:05:10,184
I’m sure they won’t be happy about this.

75
00:05:15,481 --> 00:05:16,566
Bok.

76
00:05:16,649 --> 00:05:17,692
Bok, this is not good.

77
00:05:18,359 --> 00:05:19,736
Alex, this is not good!

78
00:05:20,737 --> 00:05:23,781
Why did you still have
to tell him about our mission?

79
00:05:23,865 --> 00:05:24,824
Huh?

80
00:05:25,616 --> 00:05:27,577
Are you listening to me, Bok?

81
00:05:27,660 --> 00:05:28,578
This is not good!

82
00:05:28,661 --> 00:05:30,872
If Viktor finds out
that we’re investigating him,

83
00:05:30,955 --> 00:05:31,956
we’re both dead!

84
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:33,499
Then he’ll start targeting you, me,

85
00:05:33,583 --> 00:05:35,335
and our entire agency.

86
00:05:35,418 --> 00:05:36,586
Bok, right?

87
00:05:40,131 --> 00:05:40,965
Huh?

88
00:05:42,300 --> 00:05:43,843
Why did you even have to say that?

89
00:05:43,926 --> 00:05:46,596
That hasn’t even been approved
by our higher-ups yet!

90
00:05:48,014 --> 00:05:50,475
If we can’t use Mikoy anyway,

91
00:05:50,558 --> 00:05:52,810
might as well just silence him.

92
00:05:56,522 --> 00:05:57,356
Bok!

93
00:05:57,440 --> 00:05:58,566
Have some restraint!

94
00:05:58,649 --> 00:06:00,651
You’re going to kill a fellow Filipino?

95
00:06:00,735 --> 00:06:03,696
May I remind you, Mikoy is innocent.

96
00:06:04,697 --> 00:06:08,451
So, he has nothing to do with the things
the Moraviano has been doing.

97
00:06:08,534 --> 00:06:12,246
He became part of the syndicate the moment
he chose to protect Chiara!

98
00:06:13,414 --> 00:06:14,707
That’s why we have higher-ups.

99
00:06:14,791 --> 00:06:16,459
We cannot make that call, Alex.

100
00:06:17,085 --> 00:06:18,377
So what?

101
00:06:18,461 --> 00:06:21,047
So we’ll just let him
ruin our investigation?

102
00:07:07,468 --> 00:07:09,095
What’s the problem?

103
00:07:26,863 --> 00:07:27,780
Chiara.

104
00:07:29,824 --> 00:07:31,117
There’s something you need to know.

105
00:07:33,744 --> 00:07:35,496
What do I need to know?

106
00:07:38,666 --> 00:07:39,917
Shit!

107
00:07:45,590 --> 00:07:46,883
What’s the problem?

108
00:07:47,592 --> 00:07:48,634
Chiara.

109
00:08:40,978 --> 00:08:42,230
Sorry, but…

110
00:08:43,689 --> 00:08:46,901
I won’t be able to continue
with our plans tonight.

111
00:08:48,027 --> 00:08:49,028
There’s…

112
00:08:49,612 --> 00:08:51,113
There’s just a problem
at home all of a sudden.

113
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,074
Oh.

114
00:08:57,245 --> 00:08:58,162
Well,

115
00:08:59,539 --> 00:09:03,167
it’s okay if you don’t come with us
tonight, Mikoy.

116
00:09:05,336 --> 00:09:07,588
But I’m already part of your life now.

117
00:09:10,550 --> 00:09:12,510
Maybe I can help.

118
00:09:14,011 --> 00:09:15,513
Or at least

119
00:09:15,596 --> 00:09:18,933
I can be someone
you can talk to about your problems.

120
00:09:23,145 --> 00:09:24,355
My brother was arrested.

121
00:09:27,942 --> 00:09:31,195
In a… In an anti-drug operation.

122
00:09:31,779 --> 00:09:33,781
He was caught with drugs?

123
00:09:36,534 --> 00:09:38,953
I still don’t know the full details, but…

124
00:09:42,331 --> 00:09:43,624
Maybe it’s my fault.

125
00:09:45,710 --> 00:09:48,129
I’m the reason why
he ended up in that situation.

126
00:09:53,384 --> 00:09:55,428
Chiara, it’s too complicated.

127
00:09:58,014 --> 00:10:01,392
What I need right now
is to find a way to help him.

128
00:10:02,393 --> 00:10:04,520
Please don’t blame yourself.

129
00:10:15,531 --> 00:10:16,699
Maybe.

130
00:10:24,165 --> 00:10:25,708
Maybe he can help.

131
00:10:26,459 --> 00:10:28,252
My mom and dad have friends
in the Philippines

132
00:10:28,336 --> 00:10:30,171
who hold high positions in the government.

133
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:32,673
Maybe they can find a way.

134
00:10:32,757 --> 00:10:34,759
Friends in the Philippines?

135
00:10:35,676 --> 00:10:38,679
My mom and dad are active
in the Philippines

136
00:10:38,763 --> 00:10:40,056
because of their business.

137
00:10:43,809 --> 00:10:46,687
And through the years,
they’ve also developed relationships

138
00:10:46,771 --> 00:10:49,398
with powerful and influential people.

139
00:10:50,274 --> 00:10:51,150
So I am sure

140
00:10:52,026 --> 00:10:53,944
they can do something
to help your brother.

141
00:10:54,862 --> 00:10:55,821
Don’t.

142
00:10:57,406 --> 00:10:58,240
No.

143
00:11:01,118 --> 00:11:02,870
This is my family’s problem.

144
00:11:03,954 --> 00:11:05,414
So, let us handle it first.

145
00:11:05,498 --> 00:11:07,458
Mikoy, are you sure?

146
00:11:16,175 --> 00:11:17,927
Just remember, if you need anything…

147
00:11:25,935 --> 00:11:27,311
Thank you, Chiara.

148
00:11:30,648 --> 00:11:31,607
Thank you.

149
00:11:46,497 --> 00:11:47,456
Pair of Jacks.

150
00:11:50,209 --> 00:11:51,544
-Beat that!
-Wow!

151
00:11:51,627 --> 00:11:52,670
Fold.

152
00:12:03,806 --> 00:12:04,723
Child, it’s your turn.

153
00:12:16,527 --> 00:12:18,529
Are you getting bored
with me and your father?

154
00:12:18,612 --> 00:12:20,990
Or is something bothering you?

155
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:25,411
But yes, something is bothering me.

156
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:29,582
Care to share what it is
that’s "battering" you?

157
00:12:29,665 --> 00:12:31,083
Bothering you.

158
00:12:31,167 --> 00:12:32,710
-Ah, okay.
-Bothering you.

159
00:12:32,793 --> 00:12:34,253
-Close enough.
-Oh, okay.

160
00:12:37,214 --> 00:12:38,507
Mikoy?

161
00:12:46,223 --> 00:12:47,475
-No.
-No, Papa. No.

162
00:12:54,315 --> 00:12:56,066
It’s about his family.

163
00:12:56,692 --> 00:12:58,486
His family in the Philippines.

164
00:12:58,569 --> 00:13:00,321
Are they having financial problems?

165
00:13:01,363 --> 00:13:02,615
Mama,

166
00:13:02,698 --> 00:13:06,410
you know very well
how proud Filipinos can be.

167
00:13:06,494 --> 00:13:08,746
If it were about money,

168
00:13:08,829 --> 00:13:14,502
Mikoy would find another way first
before coming to me.

169
00:13:21,300 --> 00:13:22,551
But…

170
00:13:22,635 --> 00:13:23,886
But what?

171
00:13:24,470 --> 00:13:25,596
It’s about his younger brother.

172
00:13:25,679 --> 00:13:27,181
He got arrested.

173
00:13:27,264 --> 00:13:29,892
As far as I know, they found drugs on him.

174
00:13:33,354 --> 00:13:35,648
Oh, I feel so bad for Mikoy.

175
00:13:41,820 --> 00:13:45,115
MOM

176
00:13:53,374 --> 00:13:54,208
Hello, Ma?

177
00:13:56,669 --> 00:13:57,503
Son?

178
00:13:59,880 --> 00:14:02,216
We weren’t supposed to call you anymore,

179
00:14:02,299 --> 00:14:04,802
but your father insisted.

180
00:14:04,885 --> 00:14:08,973
He said you need to know everything
that’s happening to your brother.

181
00:14:12,101 --> 00:14:13,394
Why, what’s the problem?

182
00:14:14,353 --> 00:14:16,438
We went to Manila, son.

183
00:14:16,522 --> 00:14:19,275
We’re here at the police station.

184
00:14:19,358 --> 00:14:22,319
Your brother Angelito

185
00:14:23,153 --> 00:14:27,116
was caught during a raid at a bar.

186
00:14:27,199 --> 00:14:31,245
Oh my God, and then
they said he had drugs on him!

187
00:14:35,165 --> 00:14:39,378
Wasn’t the reason he went abroad
to send his sibling to college?

188
00:14:39,461 --> 00:14:40,546
Is that him?

189
00:14:49,013 --> 00:14:54,435
And what’s even more frustrating
is he is blaming himself for that.

190
00:14:55,269 --> 00:14:57,396
Angelito, Mom.

191
00:14:57,479 --> 00:14:58,898
How is he?

192
00:14:58,981 --> 00:15:01,692
Son, we already spoke with a lawyer

193
00:15:01,775 --> 00:15:06,739
who is studying what remedy
can be given to your brother.

194
00:15:07,740 --> 00:15:08,824
He’s okay.

195
00:15:09,575 --> 00:15:10,993
He’s comfortable here at the station.

196
00:15:11,076 --> 00:15:14,330
And the police are treating him well.

197
00:15:46,487 --> 00:15:47,780
Oh my!

198
00:16:10,177 --> 00:16:15,557
He couldn’t have done
the things they are accusing him of.

199
00:16:15,641 --> 00:16:18,060
You know your brother, right?

200
00:16:18,143 --> 00:16:20,896
He wouldn’t even hurt a fly.

201
00:16:20,980 --> 00:16:23,107
Drugs, of all things!

202
00:16:23,857 --> 00:16:25,693
Mikoy, we’re okay here, all right?

203
00:16:25,776 --> 00:16:27,069
I’ll handle it.

204
00:16:27,152 --> 00:16:28,570
But son!

205
00:16:28,654 --> 00:16:32,074
He wouldn’t ruin his life for that.

206
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:34,118
No!

207
00:16:35,244 --> 00:16:38,539
He wouldn’t throw away everything
you all have done

208
00:16:38,622 --> 00:16:41,417
for drugs.

209
00:16:41,500 --> 00:16:43,002
All right, Mikoy.

210
00:17:03,188 --> 00:17:04,565
Oh! Oh! Oh!

211
00:17:06,066 --> 00:17:06,900
It’s just me!

212
00:17:10,612 --> 00:17:13,907
Why? Why did you send these things to me?

213
00:17:13,991 --> 00:17:15,868
We need to leave as soon as possible.

214
00:17:15,951 --> 00:17:16,785
Huh?

215
00:17:21,206 --> 00:17:23,167
Our local operator
is waiting for us there,

216
00:17:23,250 --> 00:17:25,669
and he is arranging
us a flight back to Manila.

217
00:17:26,420 --> 00:17:28,213
Why didn’t you go through with it?

218
00:17:30,007 --> 00:17:31,633
Especially since we’re not in Manila.

219
00:17:32,801 --> 00:17:36,013
So what you mean is
maybe Mikoy already reported us

220
00:17:36,096 --> 00:17:37,347
to Chiara and her father?

221
00:17:40,893 --> 00:17:41,769
We need to leave.

222
00:17:44,855 --> 00:17:47,441
But do you understand what’s happening?

223
00:17:47,524 --> 00:17:52,696
So now Viktor will know that he is
being investigated by our agency,

224
00:17:52,780 --> 00:17:54,698
so he will become even more careful.

225
00:17:54,782 --> 00:17:56,700
And his surroundings
will be even more protected.

226
00:17:56,784 --> 00:17:58,494
And wait, one more thing.

227
00:17:58,577 --> 00:18:00,120
It will be very hard.

228
00:18:00,204 --> 00:18:03,957
It will be virtually impossible
to infiltrate his syndicate.

229
00:18:04,041 --> 00:18:07,753
He might even use his influence
to undermine our agency.

230
00:18:10,506 --> 00:18:13,050
We still shouldn’t stop
fighting his syndicate.

231
00:18:17,012 --> 00:18:18,514
We need to fight back

232
00:18:19,181 --> 00:18:21,266
or more people will become their victims.

233
00:18:24,436 --> 00:18:26,730
If we can’t use Mikoy,

234
00:18:27,314 --> 00:18:29,733
then we’ll just find another way.

235
00:18:30,359 --> 00:18:31,777
-Let’s go.
-Okay.

236
00:18:36,240 --> 00:18:37,783
That’s not my phone.

237
00:18:46,375 --> 00:18:47,709
This is Mikoy’s number.

238
00:18:47,793 --> 00:18:49,378
Why is he calling you now?

239
00:18:54,716 --> 00:18:56,927
I want to meet now.

240
00:18:58,137 --> 00:18:59,638
I want to talk again.

241
00:19:04,935 --> 00:19:06,395
Where are you?

242
00:19:53,400 --> 00:19:55,903
Bok, are you okay? Bok!

243
00:20:01,491 --> 00:20:02,868
What if this is just a trap by Mikoy?

244
00:20:02,951 --> 00:20:04,870
What if Viktor is only setting us up?

245
00:20:04,953 --> 00:20:05,829
Then the two of us are doomed.

246
00:20:08,707 --> 00:20:11,210
You know, you’re so overdramatic
and way too negative.

247
00:20:11,293 --> 00:20:13,295
What negative? Okay.

248
00:20:13,378 --> 00:20:15,130
The Moravianos
have homecourt advantage here.

249
00:20:15,214 --> 00:20:17,591
Like in basketball, here in Prague,

250
00:20:17,674 --> 00:20:20,510
Viktor Valtrovi
has the homecourt advantage. Okay?

251
00:20:20,594 --> 00:20:22,346
We don’t stand a chance here.

252
00:20:22,429 --> 00:20:23,513
So, if I’m overreacting,
then I’m overreacting.

253
00:20:23,597 --> 00:20:25,057
But we’re at a disadvantage
here in Prague!

254
00:20:40,906 --> 00:20:43,784
But what if Mikoy has another reason
for wanting to talk to us?

255
00:20:43,867 --> 00:20:47,579
Maybe that’s what Judas said
before he betrayed Jesus.

256
00:20:47,663 --> 00:20:51,333
That he has a reason to be able
to have dinner face-to-face with him.

257
00:20:51,416 --> 00:20:54,878
Look, if you don't want to come,
that's okay.

258
00:20:55,587 --> 00:20:57,089
I'll be the one to face him first.

259
00:20:57,172 --> 00:20:59,007
You can go back
to the surveillance van first.

260
00:20:59,091 --> 00:21:02,344
And if you don't hear
from me within an hour,

261
00:21:02,427 --> 00:21:03,971
leave Prague immediately.

262
00:21:04,054 --> 00:21:08,850
Do you think
I would let you face this alone?

263
00:21:09,601 --> 00:21:11,103
We're already here anyway.

264
00:21:11,186 --> 00:21:13,188
Do you think I would abandon you here?

265
00:21:13,272 --> 00:21:16,775
Do you think I would leave you hanging?

266
00:21:17,567 --> 00:21:19,194
We're together until the end.

267
00:21:27,119 --> 00:21:28,036
Bok, someone's here!

268
00:21:28,120 --> 00:21:29,288
Abort, abort!

269
00:21:38,797 --> 00:21:40,882
-Civilian.
-All right, all right.

270
00:21:42,592 --> 00:21:44,094
Hey! Hey! Hey!

271
00:21:44,177 --> 00:21:45,345
Wait! What's that!

272
00:21:46,430 --> 00:21:47,723
Did I do something wrong?

273
00:21:50,309 --> 00:21:51,310
Are you alone?

274
00:21:51,393 --> 00:21:52,352
Yes.

275
00:21:53,061 --> 00:21:53,895
I'm alone.

276
00:21:53,979 --> 00:21:56,773
How can we be sure that you
didn't tip Viktor off about us?

277
00:21:56,857 --> 00:21:58,483
I don't have anyone with me.

278
00:21:59,151 --> 00:22:00,193
I'm really alone.

279
00:22:03,947 --> 00:22:06,116
He's telling the truth. He's alone.

280
00:22:12,372 --> 00:22:14,750
I hope you understand that
we have to take precautions.

281
00:22:14,833 --> 00:22:16,835
Especially the last time we talked,

282
00:22:16,918 --> 00:22:19,588
I know you were determined
to report us to Viktor.

283
00:22:20,547 --> 00:22:21,840
So our assumption is,

284
00:22:22,758 --> 00:22:24,718
Viktor will make a move against us.

285
00:22:26,636 --> 00:22:28,263
But you still met with me?

286
00:22:28,346 --> 00:22:29,931
Just like I said,

287
00:22:30,891 --> 00:22:32,142
I am desperate.

288
00:22:32,893 --> 00:22:34,853
We have already tried everything
we could do

289
00:22:34,936 --> 00:22:36,605
to infiltrate the Moraviano.

290
00:22:36,688 --> 00:22:38,565
But it is really impossible.

291
00:22:38,648 --> 00:22:40,317
So when you called us,

292
00:22:40,984 --> 00:22:42,235
we had to take the risk.

293
00:22:42,319 --> 00:22:44,237
Maybe you changed your mind.

294
00:22:45,238 --> 00:22:46,531
Do I even have a choice?

295
00:22:47,074 --> 00:22:49,367
If I don't cooperate with you,

296
00:22:49,451 --> 00:22:51,036
you will ruin my brother's life!

297
00:22:51,620 --> 00:22:52,996
Like I said,

298
00:22:53,997 --> 00:22:55,749
I am desperate, Mr. Pinagpala.

299
00:22:56,625 --> 00:22:57,876
As time goes on,

300
00:22:58,460 --> 00:23:00,003
the operations of the Moraviano

301
00:23:00,087 --> 00:23:01,922
in the Philippines
are expanding and getting stronger.

302
00:23:02,005 --> 00:23:05,592
I am afraid that I have no more time left.

303
00:23:06,343 --> 00:23:08,261
I did that so that you would agree.

304
00:23:09,471 --> 00:23:10,931
So if I agree,

305
00:23:11,932 --> 00:23:13,141
my brother will be released?

306
00:23:15,685 --> 00:23:19,022
His record will be erased and cleared?

307
00:23:19,564 --> 00:23:22,067
As if nothing happened
regarding his arrest.

308
00:23:22,651 --> 00:23:24,277
Can I trust you?

309
00:23:24,861 --> 00:23:27,739
I will not risk coming here
if I were just fooling you, Mikoy.

310
00:23:41,670 --> 00:23:43,046
Tell me now,

311
00:23:43,964 --> 00:23:47,300
how did you find out
that Chiara's parents are connected

312
00:23:47,384 --> 00:23:48,343
to this syndicate?

313
00:23:55,267 --> 00:23:57,894
We don't have evidence
linking him directly,

314
00:23:58,562 --> 00:24:01,439
but we caught a low-level operative

315
00:24:01,523 --> 00:24:02,440
who we forced to talk.

316
00:24:02,524 --> 00:24:03,358
Investigate this.

317
00:24:05,360 --> 00:24:07,112
That is an import-export company

318
00:24:07,195 --> 00:24:10,490
used by the Moraviano
for all of their operations.

319
00:24:10,574 --> 00:24:11,825
How?

320
00:24:14,035 --> 00:24:17,080
On the surface, this import-export company
looks legitimate.

321
00:24:17,164 --> 00:24:18,748
Unfortunately,

322
00:24:18,832 --> 00:24:21,001
no one can easily get inside this company.

323
00:24:24,087 --> 00:24:27,132
And the last informant we placed inside

324
00:24:28,550 --> 00:24:29,384
was killed.

325
00:24:29,467 --> 00:24:30,677
Wait.

326
00:24:31,720 --> 00:24:33,555
So if I become your informant,

327
00:24:34,723 --> 00:24:35,891
that means

328
00:24:36,933 --> 00:24:38,226
my days are numbered too?

329
00:24:39,978 --> 00:24:41,438
What do you mean it won't happen?

330
00:24:41,521 --> 00:24:42,898
It already happened to someone!

331
00:24:44,900 --> 00:24:45,817
Huh?

332
00:24:46,359 --> 00:24:47,569
How am I different?

333
00:24:47,652 --> 00:24:49,863
Their only daughter loves you.

334
00:24:50,822 --> 00:24:51,823
Chiara loves you.

335
00:24:51,907 --> 00:24:53,909
And if you really love Chiara,

336
00:24:53,992 --> 00:24:55,535
you will do this for her.

337
00:24:57,579 --> 00:24:59,956
Because sooner or later,
if you do nothing,

338
00:25:00,040 --> 00:25:02,959
she will get dragged into the mess
her family is making.

339
00:25:05,045 --> 00:25:07,088
This life is really so difficult!

340
00:25:13,470 --> 00:25:14,512
What do you need me to do?

341
00:25:15,263 --> 00:25:18,141
You go in tomorrow, as if we never met.

342
00:25:47,545 --> 00:25:48,421
Mikoy!

343
00:25:59,557 --> 00:26:01,059
Mikoy, my child,

344
00:26:01,142 --> 00:26:03,687
I have good news for you.

345
00:26:03,770 --> 00:26:05,272
What is happening?

346
00:26:05,355 --> 00:26:07,732
Mikoy, your brother has been released.

347
00:26:08,316 --> 00:26:11,361
And the police said
they will not file charges.

348
00:26:12,946 --> 00:26:15,073
Isn't that wonderful news, my child?

349
00:26:15,156 --> 00:26:16,908
Thank God!

350
00:26:16,992 --> 00:26:20,161
And my child, thanks also to Sir Kian.

351
00:26:21,162 --> 00:26:22,205
Sir Kian?

352
00:26:22,789 --> 00:26:26,584
Kian is the police officer
handling your brother's case.

353
00:26:26,668 --> 00:26:29,504
And he was the one who talked to them
not to pursue the case.

354
00:26:29,587 --> 00:26:31,548
Angelito is also a victim.

355
00:26:31,631 --> 00:26:33,925
May I speak with Mikoy?

356
00:26:34,009 --> 00:26:34,884
Ah…

357
00:26:35,885 --> 00:26:37,178
Hello. Um…

358
00:26:37,262 --> 00:26:38,638
Mikoy, wait, someone
wants to speak with you.

359
00:26:38,722 --> 00:26:39,556
Yes of course, sir!

360
00:26:39,639 --> 00:26:42,017
You can also explain it to him.

361
00:26:42,100 --> 00:26:43,101
Hello, Mikoy?

362
00:26:43,184 --> 00:26:45,145
This is your Sir Kian.

363
00:26:45,228 --> 00:26:50,191
I feel like I already know you
from all the stories I’ve heard about you.

364
00:26:50,275 --> 00:26:52,819
But anyway, don’t worry anymore.

365
00:26:52,902 --> 00:26:54,529
Your brother has been cleared.

366
00:26:55,113 --> 00:26:58,116
Just remind him to stay away from trouble.

367
00:26:58,199 --> 00:27:00,952
Because next time,
he might end up in jail.

368
00:27:02,662 --> 00:27:06,791
Good thing he has a family who loves him.

369
00:27:08,418 --> 00:27:11,296
And a very supportive brother.

370
00:27:12,464 --> 00:27:13,923
Thank you, Sir Kian.

371
00:27:14,007 --> 00:27:15,133
You're welcome.

372
00:27:34,986 --> 00:27:37,364
He is the one making sure
that Angelito will be released.

373
00:27:37,447 --> 00:27:40,116
And that they will not
file any case against him.

374
00:27:46,331 --> 00:27:48,041
So now, Mikoy,

375
00:27:50,001 --> 00:27:51,127
you help me.

376
00:28:07,519 --> 00:28:08,395
Have you read everything?

377
00:28:08,478 --> 00:28:11,689
I am voluntarily coordinating
with your agency.

378
00:28:11,773 --> 00:28:17,779
You need to find a way
to put this in Donabel and Viktor’s room.

379
00:28:17,862 --> 00:28:20,990
Anyone in my place
would definitely be afraid, right?

380
00:28:21,074 --> 00:28:24,494
I don’t know about you,
but I don’t want to die too soon.

381
00:28:24,494 --> 00:28:25,494
MkvDrama.net
